{
  "stem": "20089.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when the American congressmen came, and Miss Richman took them through to the dormitories, she was as disgusted as I was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, I was in the-- Miss Richman, myself, and Abram, and the congressmen were taken through to the-- to the dormitories.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was absolute bedlam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was ugly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the beds weren't made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The cushions were on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The cupboards were dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was dust all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I realized, again, to my horror and frustration, that the Jewish Agency were behind it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't make-- I couldn't make any excuses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Miss Richman I think made some excuses-- excuses to the American congressmen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in their politeness, they thanked us and left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But Miss Richman, actually, at that stage was very angry with-- with Abram because she said that she had put her-- he had put her in disgrace, that she wasn't able to keep the place clean.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he explained the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I think she understood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But she nevertheless felt that she-- she was actually not assisted by Abram, but she was sabotaged by him and the other Jewish Agency people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I think in retrospect, again, what he did was in order to get as many immigrants to Palestine, and not to the outside world, to the rest of the world.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I couldn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But Miss Richman and Andy were more mature than me, and certainly Abram was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was accepted by them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think those sort of clashes that I had with the Jewish Agency, because I really wasn't as honest at that stage.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was more interested in my professionalism and my moral attitudes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that's due-- that was due to my immaturity, not to my maturity.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
